{"tid":108584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[家變] 如果發現老母做左人地2奶","createTime":"2017-02-05T11:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T16:51:28.000Z","uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4defc0ca64088fa09237e283d2c75fafbfddefb8","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"我自己就單親家庭既 半年前老母同個男人行得好埋<br />\n我亦唔反對有新老豆 但近幾個月開始聽到d唔係咁好既野<br />\n一開始我聽到佢有仔女 咁我就以為佢都係單親啦 冇所謂<br />\n但愈聽愈多 發現佢仲有老婆 而我老母都知 <br />\n甚至連我呀婆都知 所有人都好似睇唔到佢地一齊左咁 <br />\n個男人表面上好好 好努力追我老母 而我當初都好滿意呢個男人 <br />\n但我估唔到佢背景原來係咁多野係我唔知<br />\n而我老母到目前為止都冇同我講過一粒字有關於個男人<br />\n只係叫我叫佢做叔叔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我仲係學生 就畢業 未搵到第一份糧 唔敢問老母怕家變<br />\n各位巴打我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男人差唔多1個月就上黎我屋企1個星期 屋企細 我唔想知2個加埋成百歲係間房到做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFYI: 老豆老母岩岩分開冇耐 老母開始識跟人周圍去玩 當初有男人話包佢做2奶 我老母都say no 我真係好感動 <br />\n我好難想像今次老母竟然會咁做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸： 老母好搵得錢 根本唔需要比任何人包起2奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7525f1790181462fa1ad201f3456e4b186292dbd","tid":108584,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"你呀媽搵到錢養到你<br />\n佢又自願做人二奶 <br />\n咁關你咩事"},{"pid":"9773e0b93449b6b83199f851cc79ca935c34678d","tid":108584,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"係咪女人都想要 被人愛既感覺"},{"pid":"55442c1bc531685914119231d1c3f79f8f8dae62","tid":108584,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪女人都想要 被人愛既感覺</blockquote><br />\n幾廿歲人都唔撚化既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09172c3f31ef1592ae7559139959b14ffd8de1c0","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呀媽搵到錢養到你<br />\n佢又自願做人二奶 <br />\n咁關你咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係接受唔到有個咁既老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我日日係屋企都黑哂面 好撚想喊出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a20569a979eef6a8de16183c2e0f1e6d13a4f22","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪女人都想要 被人愛既感覺</blockquote><br />\n幾廿歲人都唔撚化既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔就最憎第三者 咁樣既愛 唔要就把撚啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0e1dab6b2ca66b6a995c6ca6838c3353a275fc","tid":108584,"uid":59327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"以不變應萬變"},{"pid":"d2be70828d6b868b691d6e1d0c188fe85e7e09e0","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以不變應萬變</blockquote><br />\n我怕我頂唔順 我而加日日都屈住呢個問題好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1692467f150e23970b8c3c96abdf3724486eec60","tid":108584,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你呀媽搵到錢養到你<br />\n佢又自願做人二奶 <br />\n咁關你咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係接受唔到有個咁既老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我日日係屋企都黑哂面 好撚想喊出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接受唔到咪唔好接受囉<br />\n你呀媽又冇逼你叫佢老豆"},{"pid":"5d8f9e21f440ab27ab727b41f3be5445b82cf486","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你呀媽搵到錢養到你<br />\n佢又自願做人二奶 <br />\n咁關你咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係接受唔到有個咁既老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我日日係屋企都黑哂面 好撚想喊出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接受唔到咪唔好接受囉<br />\n你呀媽又冇逼你叫佢老豆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係一個好開放既人 但我老母而加做人2奶 條氣邊到順 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果條仔真係普通單親家庭男人 我唔會介意叫老豆 再認埋多個妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa4f659ad074cfbb2a9f276d2c0f82f588aefd2","tid":108584,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"搵到錢咪當佢叫鴨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93454ad50b052a2b125e453b29aa24adecf493e1","tid":108584,"uid":69751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"係愛呀哈利"},{"pid":"fd6298beadec0638a0218ff37449bd30400dae61","tid":108584,"uid":73112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"食人妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d78b1e04d0b5f6072a0ef0cb3400fba400bd3d1","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係愛呀哈利</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a1d1e42538dd6056dc836ced71319210487890","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵到錢咪當佢叫鴨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫鴨都還好 而加玩真感情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7bec130b2039f085311da23840256e6742ed42","tid":108584,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"調查下呀媽同個男人點識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  既然你話呀媽搵得到錢既 咁會唔會個男人想埋身借伯母賺番筆呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c5d516f006bda3f429463665a2d6c94968ea75","tid":108584,"uid":47383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4c5d8e7a63d8e21d321abcd72fbf0c77cd913a","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>調查下呀媽同個男人點識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  既然你話呀媽搵得到錢既 咁會唔會個男人想埋身借伯母賺番筆呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該就唔會話要錢 條仔有車有樓 <br />\n我老母同條仔係咩 中小學聚會識 你話幾耐之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb5871bbc24cdc90c9c57e48e488886bb687302","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食人妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b0abcb27536594994a597fa18948da4d0bb7e6","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7bca53597f9fbf58f395e1e94fd4ebbe293c9f6a","tid":108584,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">家門不幸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"cf4