s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果條仔真係普通單親家庭男人 我唔會介意叫老豆 再認埋多個妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢上你阿媽，你上返佢個女以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c1787b1eead30f4a21fb3d014c807bd43c7055","tid":108584,"uid":9188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"佢開心咪得囉<br />\n你講到你老母咁有錢<br />\n可能佢都係想搵個人陪下姐<br />\n最緊要係仲錫你咪得囉"},{"pid":"a38ac2d4e5c51a6e09c6da6f09d8c20c7a2c49b6","tid":108584,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"萬一你做兵，你老母睇怕一樣阻止唔到。勸你都係睇開啲啦"},{"pid":"3d4d3cfa578f9ae39ed122d4d9116cb0fe6894f9","tid":108584,"uid":25717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"屌 樓主個case同我好撚似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾年老母成日帶個男人番屋企<br />\n言談間知道個男人有仔女有埋孫<br />\n老母又係叫我稱呼佢做「叔叔」<br />\n「叔叔」又會成日比錢我洗<br />\n對我地幾好係真<br />\n不過我始終開唔到口問老母同叔叔咩關係 係咪做人二奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9060105ecfd3b6920a09b18ec193bcc1518d8d1b","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接受唔到咪唔好接受囉<br />\n你呀媽又冇逼你叫佢老豆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係一個好開放既人 但我老母而加做人2奶 條氣邊到順 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果條仔真係普通單親家庭男人 我唔會介意叫老豆 再認埋多個妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢上你阿媽，你上返佢個女以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港定律： 每個床下都有個社工係到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd47c20f36d71d66b6c34bb6d0033eb47ef5b969","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢開心咪得囉<br />\n你講到你老母咁有錢<br />\n可能佢都係想搵個人陪下姐<br />\n最緊要係仲錫你咪得囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都岩 <br />\n只係我過唔到自己心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14673ab746e78e9a4753e3351f9b896c42fd8f26","tid":108584,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"大家都成年人喇<br />\n<br />\n大人既事交番俾佢地自己解決喇"},{"pid":"fd854d17bf785be2e911668f0d3df745314a75e6","tid":108584,"uid":2455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"證明你老母仲有市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你應該開心先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9171f7463f6ec4e2fcf687b64b0051cb559fb41","tid":108584,"uid":53011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"正常有家室男人點可以一個月有四分一時間唔番屋企<br />\n<br />\n睇到你話老母搵到錢就有個想法:<br />\n可能佢係當打份工送下外賣 佢老婆仔女都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bff2f8fd7416f8c84d858dc0ad405ad2dd3980a","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 樓主個case同我好撚似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾年老母成日帶個男人番屋企<br />\n言談間知道個男人有仔女有埋孫<br />\n老母又係叫我稱呼佢做「叔叔」<br />\n「叔叔」又會成日比錢我洗<br />\n對我地幾好係真<br />\n不過我始終開唔到口問老母同叔叔咩關係 係咪做人二奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3028f76ff568952324d72df9ed4f1d2f59bfd3f3","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明你老母仲有市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你應該開心先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母一直都好多人追 但又唔係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f715329a215732ef732831df955a3855f156a81e","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常有家室男人點可以一個月有四分一時間唔番屋企<br />\n<br />\n睇到你話老母搵到錢就有個想法:<br />\n可能佢係當打份工送下外賣 佢老婆仔女都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺呀 佢可以完全斯唔洗理d仔女老婆 成日搵我老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c7ba480a539c1fe1280f27392ffb00d0d980f0","tid":108584,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"樓主男定女"},{"pid":"38f4f836490f1db424338795962fd23a8a0a79fa","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主男定女</blockquote><br />\n男 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4d58fda71b27a5d79c84cee817bc22405680c2","tid":108584,"uid":19385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以不變應萬變</blockquote><br />\n我怕我頂唔順 我而加日日都屈住呢個問題好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感情事好難講對與錯，你唔支持都平常心對待就ok."},{"pid":"f229de9a3f285ebeccea34fed04c24806d0615e0","tid":108584,"uid":25646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"我老母都係 不過佢地好少見<br />\n個男人有仔女 廿幾歲既有 幾歲既都有<br />\n我老母叫我嗌佢做叔叔<br />\n有時佢地傾電話 叔叔成日好關心我<br />\n想同我傾電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我老母有好坦白同我講<br />\n老豆對佢唔好 維持左呢個家廿幾年都係因為有我係到 如果唔係一早走左 佢好想我支持佢<br />\n咁其實諗深一層 如果老母開心 咩都係值得<br />\n愛係冇分對錯 巴打你向好果方面諗下<br />\n其實只要佢開心 作為仔女應該鄧佢開心先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adad388ac7a8a6bd7934f5195fca17c26ff8aea","tid":108584,"uid":16718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>調查下呀媽同個男人點識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  既然你話呀媽搵得到錢既 咁會唔會個男人想埋身借伯母賺番筆呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該就唔會話要錢 條仔有車有樓 <br />\n我老母同條仔係咩 中小學聚會識 你話幾耐之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中小學...即係識咗好耐，可能係大家的初戀etc<br />\n重拾愛火...呢d真係好難甩，唯有咁，看開d<br />\n呢個係你母親的決定，佢自己要承擔決定帶來的後果。"},{"pid":"673aa1f8a8102777aac537bf709232bc64ce341d","tid":108584,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"我表姐都係咁 做緊人二奶<br />\n個男人個老婆唔肯離婚 <br />\n之前表姐帶佢黎同班親戚食飯大家都勁尷尬<br />\n不過佢好愛個男人 可以點 由得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef1438cc40fec547c96b5c0d239fb4d0bb285dc","tid":108584,"uid":38703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你呀媽搵到錢養到你<br />\n佢又自願做人二奶 <br />\n咁關你咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係接受唔到有個咁既老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我日日係屋企都黑哂面 好撚想喊出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你以後要接受有人要屌你老母喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1334316c45ea2d1a37471c53f9800c273bafdfa","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你呀媽搵到錢養到你<br />\n佢又自願做人二奶 <br />\n咁關你咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係接受唔到有個咁既老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我日日係屋企都黑哂面 好撚想喊出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你以後要接受有人要屌你老母喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋細真係惡頂"},{"pid":"b1774fd7809308ea662b787953933ca20d285c8e","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>調查下呀媽同個男人點識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  既然你話呀媽搵得到錢既 咁會唔會個男人想埋身借伯母賺番筆呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該就唔會話要錢 條仔有車有樓 <br />\n我老母同條仔係咩 中小學聚會識 你話幾耐之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中小學...即係識咗好耐，可能係大家的初戀etc<br />\n重拾愛火...呢d真係好難甩，唯有咁，看開d<br />\n呢個係你母親的決定，佢自己要承擔決定帶來的後果。</blockquote><br />\n就係唔想老母比人千夫所指 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc523ec2ec8a0987b8fd1cf0931b9d13f43d24a","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我表姐都係咁 做緊人二奶<br />\n個男人個老婆唔肯離婚 <br />\n之前表姐帶佢黎同班親戚食飯大家都勁尷尬<br />\n不過佢好愛個男人 可以點 由得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老母已經帶埋佢過年周圍去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知d人用咩目光睇我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a255a390f42d9687ac2a846b52348773e719bac","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老母都係 不過佢地好少見<br />\n個男人有仔女 廿幾歲既有 幾歲既都有<br />\n我老母叫我嗌佢做叔叔<br />\n有時佢地傾電話 叔叔成日好關心我<br />\n想同我傾電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我老母有好坦白同我講<br />\n老豆對佢唔好 維持左呢個家廿幾年都係因為有我係到 如果唔係一早走左 佢好想我支持佢<br />\n咁其實諗深一層 如果老母開心 咩都係值得<br />\n愛係冇分對錯 巴打你向好果方面諗下<br />\n其實只要佢開心 作為仔女應該鄧佢開心先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我個個唔見就煲電話粥 一見就成個星期 <br />\n你老母有同你講叫好 我老母一粒字都冇提過 <br />\n而加做左個心理關口比我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想老母開心 但我唔想老母就咁行錯路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22652c832ebff6a7fce727262f38f14240844fb","tid":108584,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:47:38.000Z","msg":"先下手為強 搞大你阿媽個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5df42180e8bcc5f1095fcbcbc6553c62ad371a0","tid":108584,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"你講得兩個人加埋成百歲，<br />\n即係佢地都有四五十歲，人到左呢個年紀，<br />\n都仍然決定咁做，<br />\n你估佢地唔知道有咩後果，<br />\n會發咩野事咩？<br />\n<br />\n你覺得好大件事，<br />\n其實喺佢地眼中你認為重要咩？<br />\n<br />\n學激戰張家輝話齋&quot;唔重要啦！～&quot;<br />\n<br />\n你話怕人指指點點，<br />\n係你阿媽怕定你怕先？<br />\n你如果真係愛你阿媽，<br />\n你只需要同佢講，佢認為開心就支持佢就夠架啦"},{"pid":"c2713743220dc5e22242f4ab83bbe9d72c7ec856","tid":108584,"uid":9515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接受唔到咪唔好接受囉<br />\n你呀媽又冇逼你叫佢老豆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係一個好開放既人 但我老母而加做人2奶 條氣邊到順 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果條仔真係普通單親家庭男人 我唔會介意叫老豆 再認埋多個妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢上你阿媽，你上返佢個女以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢位師兄就講得岩喇"},{"pid":"b24b82a782fe752544fa6005a19a8da98266fa6a","tid":108584,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係一個好開放既人 但我老母而加做人2奶 條氣邊到順 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果條仔真係普通單親家庭男人 我唔會介意叫老豆 再認埋多個妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢上你阿媽，你上返佢個女以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢位師兄就講得岩喇</blockquote><br />\n會上A1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}